      Instrument Overview
      ===================
      The Photometry and Polarimetry Network (PPN) of the IHW
      collected data from 23 unique (telescope,instrument)
      combinations.  Both photoelectric photometers and CCD
      detectors were used.
 
      See Sekanina (1991) [&apos;JPL D-400-450&apos;] for a description
      of the various observing systems used, as far as they
      were known.

